WEBVTT

00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:02.230
Hot mics picked up their discussion.

00:00:02.240 --> 00:00:03.429
They were talking about organ

00:00:03.439 --> 00:00:04.950
transplants and the possibility that

00:00:04.960 --> 00:00:06.950
humans could live to be 150 years old.

00:00:06.960 --> 00:00:10.790
They were trying to create superhumans.

00:00:10.800 --> 00:00:13.749
It was a race involving China and other countries—though the

00:00:13.749 --> 00:00:13.759
Lord said

00:00:13.759 --> 00:00:15.669
not to mention the other

00:00:15.679 --> 00:00:18.630
country. They were taking DNA from an

00:00:18.640 --> 00:00:22.230
animal using AI. For example, how does a

00:00:22.240 --> 00:00:24.870
tortoise or a turtle live so long?

00:00:24.880 --> 00:00:26.870
They were taking that DNA and trying

00:00:26.870 --> 00:00:26.880
to use

00:00:26.880 --> 00:00:29.830
AI to splice it

00:00:29.840 --> 00:00:34.389
with human DNA, trying to create organs

00:00:34.389 --> 00:00:34.399
with

00:00:34.399 --> 00:00:36.709
longevity,

00:00:36.709 --> 00:00:36.719
specifically

00:00:36.719 --> 00:00:55.830
longevity of hearts.

00:00:55.840 --> 00:00:57.830
I'll stem this from what the Word of

00:00:57.840 --> 00:01:01.029
God says: that as the days of Noah were, so

00:01:01.039 --> 00:01:02.790
will it be when the Son of Man returns.

00:01:02.800 --> 00:01:04.789
It talks about how there

00:01:04.789 --> 00:01:04.799
were

00:01:04.799 --> 00:01:07.910
giants in the land; the angels slept

00:01:07.920 --> 00:01:09.990
with women and created giants,

00:01:10.000 --> 00:01:12.469
the Nephilim.

00:01:14.240 --> 00:01:18.469
What I saw

00:01:18.479 --> 00:01:23.429
happening in labs in certain cities

00:01:23.439 --> 00:01:26.789
was the

00:01:26.799 --> 00:01:28.469
creepiest thing I've ever seen. They

00:01:28.479 --> 00:01:32.469
were trying to create superhumans

00:01:32.469 --> 00:01:32.479
by

00:01:32.479 --> 00:01:36.390
taking DNA from an animal

00:01:36.400 --> 00:01:38.789
using AI.

00:01:38.799 --> 00:01:42.069
Since

00:01:42.079 --> 00:01:44.550
some turtles are

00:01:44.550 --> 00:01:44.560
200 to

00:01:44.560 --> 00:01:46.550
300 years old,

00:01:46.560 --> 00:01:48.870
they were taking that DNA

00:01:48.880 --> 00:01:51.350
and using AI

00:01:51.350 --> 00:01:51.360
to

00:01:51.360 --> 00:01:55.270
splice it with human DNA to

00:01:55.280 --> 00:01:59.350
create organs with longevity,

00:02:03.040 --> 00:02:07.109
trying to outsmart God.

00:02:07.119 --> 00:02:08.710
And the Lord told me, 'I

00:02:08.720 --> 00:02:10.790
fearfully and wonderfully made you in my

00:02:10.790 --> 00:02:10.800
image.'They're

00:02:10.800 --> 00:02:14.229
trying to do exactly

00:02:14.239 --> 00:02:17.589
what they did in the days

00:02:17.589 --> 00:02:17.599
of

00:02:17.599 --> 00:02:21.270
Noah. Satan was trying to destroy

00:02:21.280 --> 00:02:24.710
the bloodline of a pure human by

00:02:24.720 --> 00:02:26.309
creating

00:02:26.319 --> 00:02:28.229
monsters.

00:02:28.239 --> 00:02:30.229
The Lord showed me and said, 'As in

00:02:30.239 --> 00:02:32.070
the days of Noah, Brandon, look what

00:02:32.080 --> 00:02:33.750
they're going to do again.'They're

00:02:33.750 --> 00:02:33.760
trying

00:02:33.760 --> 00:02:36.869
to recreate the human the way

00:02:36.879 --> 00:02:40.390
we are by being blasphemous.

00:02:40.400 --> 00:02:42.869
The Lord said, 'We are

00:02:42.879 --> 00:02:45.190
made in His image; we're perfect

00:02:45.200 --> 00:02:47.270
in His sight.'When man

00:02:47.280 --> 00:02:49.990
tries to add to or take away from

00:02:50.000 --> 00:02:53.589
the DNA of a human, it

00:02:53.599 --> 00:02:55.990
takes away from who we are with God, as

00:02:55.990 --> 00:02:56.000
if

00:02:56.000 --> 00:02:57.350
saying, 'We're

00:02:57.360 --> 00:03:00.470
crossbreeds; we're not full

00:03:00.480 --> 00:03:02.309
humans.'I

00:03:02.319 --> 00:03:04.309
hope this is

00:03:04.319 --> 00:03:06.710
making sense.

00:03:08.319 --> 00:03:10.390
When I'm looking into the vision,

00:03:10.400 --> 00:03:12.550
the Lord shows me

00:03:14.159 --> 00:03:15.509
they're playing

00:03:15.519 --> 00:03:17.830
with fire. They're playing with

00:03:17.840 --> 00:03:19.670
things they don't understand, and these

00:03:19.680 --> 00:03:21.750
people have a reprobate

00:03:21.760 --> 00:03:25.350
mind. I saw them adding to the DNA,

00:03:25.360 --> 00:03:28.070
trying to make people super strong by

00:03:28.080 --> 00:03:31.110
adding genes from big

00:03:31.120 --> 00:03:33.990
gorillas

00:03:34.000 --> 00:03:37.270
to make super soldiers like

00:03:37.280 --> 00:03:38.789
Arnold Schwarzenegger.

00:03:40.640 --> 00:03:42.390
Braden told me,

00:03:46.400 --> 00:03:49.110
'Daddy, they say they've

00:03:49.120 --> 00:03:50.949
already had this for five or six years

00:03:50.959 --> 00:03:52.149
now.'Folks,

00:03:52.159 --> 00:03:54.070
I don't know anything about all

00:03:54.080 --> 00:03:56.149
that stuff. I'm not into conspiracy

00:03:56.159 --> 00:03:57.990
theories; I'm telling you what I got

00:03:58.000 --> 00:04:00.470
strictly from the voice of the Father

00:04:00.480 --> 00:04:01.990
warning about this. People

00:04:01.990 --> 00:04:02.000
talk about

00:04:02.000 --> 00:04:03.350
Alex Jones

00:04:03.350 --> 00:04:03.360
or

00:04:03.360 --> 00:04:04.789
Joe Rogan,

00:04:04.789 --> 00:04:04.799
but

00:04:04.799 --> 00:04:07.350
this is what the Spirit

00:04:07.360 --> 00:04:08.710
of the Lord said:

00:04:08.720 --> 00:04:11.030
I'm telling you what I

00:04:11.040 --> 00:04:12.869
saw in labs. If that's what they're

00:04:12.879 --> 00:04:14.949
telling you, then they're right.

00:04:14.959 --> 00:04:17.670
It was a

00:04:17.680 --> 00:04:20.390
race between China and other countries

00:04:25.440 --> 00:04:27.830
to perfect it—like

00:04:27.830 --> 00:04:27.840
a

00:04:27.840 --> 00:04:30.310
new industrial revolution

00:04:30.320 --> 00:04:33.670
with CRISPR, trying to create a new

00:04:33.680 --> 00:04:36.790
species

00:04:36.800 --> 00:04:39.749
of genetically altered human

00:04:39.749 --> 00:04:39.759
beings

00:04:39.759 --> 00:04:41.990
to get the flaws out.

00:04:44.160 --> 00:04:49.350
I saw babies in labs in

00:04:49.350 --> 00:04:49.360
amniotic

00:04:49.360 --> 00:04:52.310
fluid with a

00:04:52.320 --> 00:04:54.390
light behind them. It looked like a hot

00:04:54.400 --> 00:04:57.749
light keeping the baby warm,

00:04:57.759 --> 00:04:59.749
like something in a sci-fi movie.

00:05:05.680 --> 00:05:07.670
You could see it

00:05:07.680 --> 00:05:10.710
wasn't fully developed yet; I could

00:05:10.720 --> 00:05:12.950
see the nose and the head and how it all

00:05:12.960 --> 00:05:15.029
separates from the egg and the

00:05:15.039 --> 00:05:17.270
sperm—life

00:05:17.280 --> 00:05:20.070
without a mother.

00:05:20.080 --> 00:05:21.749
It was successful.

00:05:21.759 --> 00:05:23.990
It was alive in

00:05:24.000 --> 00:05:27.189
a

00:05:27.199 --> 00:05:28.950
cylinder tube,

00:05:28.960 --> 00:05:32.310
suspended in this

00:05:32.310 --> 00:05:32.320
amniotic

00:05:32.320 --> 00:05:35.110
fluid with real bubbles

00:05:35.120 --> 00:05:37.350
moving around this

00:05:37.360 --> 00:05:39.670
human life. The amniotic fluid had a yellow tint, almost like a shade of urine, and it looked thick like jelly. The baby was suspended in

00:05:39.670 --> 00:05:39.680
this tube being grown in a lab, and

00:05:39.680 --> 00:05:42.629
I could

00:05:42.639 --> 00:05:45.110
see

00:06:09.199 --> 00:06:11.189
an

00:06:11.189 --> 00:06:11.199
umbilical-like

00:06:11.199 --> 00:06:13.189
cord

00:06:13.199 --> 00:06:18.390
attached to this fetus. To

00:06:22.240 --> 00:06:27.749
my left in the vision, I saw six-foot-tall

00:06:27.749 --> 00:06:27.759
human-looking

00:06:27.759 --> 00:06:32.390
things

00:06:32.400 --> 00:06:35.270
that were not all human. They were

00:06:35.280 --> 00:06:37.830
spliced together, part

00:06:37.840 --> 00:06:42.790
animal and part human, with no

00:06:42.800 --> 00:06:45.110
soul in their eyes. Their eyes were

00:06:45.120 --> 00:06:48.230
completely black; unlike our eyes with a

00:06:48.240 --> 00:06:50.790
white center and

00:06:50.790 --> 00:06:50.800
an

00:06:50.800 --> 00:06:52.870
iris,

00:06:52.880 --> 00:06:55.189
they had nothing.

00:06:55.199 --> 00:06:57.430
The Lord told me,

00:06:57.440 --> 00:07:00.710
'They don't have a

00:07:00.720 --> 00:07:03.029
spirit or a

00:07:03.039 --> 00:07:05.670
soul; this is

00:07:05.680 --> 00:07:08.710
possessed by a demonic

00:07:08.710 --> 00:07:08.720
spirit.'They

00:07:10.790 --> 00:07:10.800
were

00:07:10.800 --> 00:07:12.710
splicing

00:07:12.720 --> 00:07:16.230
animal and human

00:07:16.230 --> 00:07:16.240
DNA

00:07:16.240 --> 00:07:19.189
to harvest

00:07:19.199 --> 00:07:21.270
organs,

00:07:21.280 --> 00:07:24.070
creating these things because they

00:07:24.070 --> 00:07:24.080
wanted to

00:07:24.080 --> 00:07:27.110
get a 'super

00:07:34.639 --> 00:07:36.070
heart'or

00:07:43.840 --> 00:07:45.830
harvest their

00:07:45.840 --> 00:07:47.589
livers and kidneys.

00:07:47.589 --> 00:07:47.599
They

00:07:47.599 --> 00:07:50.150
looked

00:07:50.160 --> 00:07:53.029
like monsters.

00:07:54.720 --> 00:07:57.749
The Lord said they

00:07:57.759 --> 00:08:01.189
will

00:08:01.189 --> 00:08:01.199
try

00:08:01.199 --> 00:08:03.510
to bring back

00:08:03.520 --> 00:08:06.629
prehistoric animals in the days ahead. It

00:08:06.639 --> 00:08:08.869
will become a place where you go to a

00:08:08.879 --> 00:08:12.230
zoo to see

00:08:12.240 --> 00:08:13.990
a woolly mammoth or a

00:08:14.000 --> 00:08:16.390
saber-tooth tiger. I saw them

00:08:16.400 --> 00:08:19.990
trying to find DNA, like in Jurassic Park,

00:08:20.000 --> 00:08:23.270
to create

00:08:23.280 --> 00:08:26.230
ancient dinosaurs and lizards.

00:08:26.240 --> 00:08:29.270
There

00:08:29.280 --> 00:08:31.990
is

00:08:32.000 --> 00:08:34.870
very demonic activity with AI

00:08:34.880 --> 00:08:37.350
technology in this new industrial

00:08:37.360 --> 00:08:40.149
revolution.

00:08:42.310 --> 00:08:42.320
It's

00:08:43.440 --> 00:08:47.030
an AI race, like the

00:08:47.030 --> 00:08:47.040
space race,

00:08:47.040 --> 00:08:49.990
to see

00:08:49.990 --> 00:08:50.000
who could

00:08:50.000 --> 00:08:52.710
be the first to create

00:08:52.720 --> 00:08:55.110
human cloning and

00:08:56.959 --> 00:08:59.990
superhumans.

00:09:02.320 --> 00:09:04.710
It was very dark,

00:09:04.710 --> 00:09:04.720
with

00:09:04.720 --> 00:09:07.350
people trying to be the best at

00:09:07.360 --> 00:09:09.670
splicing and making a

00:09:09.670 --> 00:09:09.680
'better'human.

00:09:09.680 --> 00:09:11.590
The Lord showed me it was like

00:09:11.600 --> 00:09:14.949
