00:09:14.959 --> 00:09:18.630
As AI

00:09:18.630 --> 00:09:18.640
is

00:09:18.640 --> 00:09:21.509
developed,

00:09:21.519 --> 00:09:23.590
there is nothing humans feel

00:09:23.590 --> 00:09:23.600
they can't

00:09:23.600 --> 00:09:26.790
achieve with technology. The veil that

00:09:26.800 --> 00:09:28.630
blocked things in the past is being

00:09:28.640 --> 00:09:32.150
lifted through technological

00:09:32.160 --> 00:09:34.790
advancements,

00:09:34.800 --> 00:09:36.870
and the darkness is

00:09:36.880 --> 00:09:39.990
becoming more real than we've ever seen

00:09:40.000 --> 00:09:41.750
it before.

00:09:43.839 --> 00:09:46.550
Gross darkness. And I'm telling

00:09:46.560 --> 00:09:48.470
you, when you start hearing about these

00:09:48.480 --> 00:09:51.030
animals going into zoos in the

00:09:51.040 --> 00:09:53.030
