00:10:05.200 --> 00:10:07.350
hearts and this stuff to the public. I

00:10:07.360 --> 00:10:10.630
don't know. I just saw that they

00:10:10.630 --> 00:10:10.640
were

00:10:10.640 --> 00:10:12.550
trying to find out the

00:10:12.560 --> 00:10:14.790
fountain of youth. How do we live

00:10:14.800 --> 00:10:17.910
longer? How did Noah live so long? I was

00:10:17.920 --> 00:10:20.069
hearing them say, "How did

00:10:20.079 --> 00:10:23.350
these men and women live

00:10:23.360 --> 00:10:26.550
so long in Bible times, a thousand years like

00:10:26.550 --> 00:10:26.560
Methuselah

00:10:26.560 --> 00:10:29.910
