00:10:29.920 --> 00:10:33.430
trying to figure out how to recreate

00:10:33.440 --> 00:10:35.829
what they had in Bible times of

00:10:35.839 --> 00:10:39.110
making people live so long

00:10:39.120 --> 00:10:41.350
because they know that our

00:10:41.360 --> 00:10:44.470
bodies are made to live and not die.

00:10:44.480 --> 00:10:46.550
God never designed us for death; that

00:10:46.560 --> 00:10:48.470
was after the fall of man. Adam would

00:10:48.480 --> 00:10:50.949
