00:10:53.120 --> 00:10:55.430
up, and they're trying to figure out how

00:10:55.440 --> 00:10:58.310
to keep the body going for a long time

00:10:58.320 --> 00:11:01.190
for these elites. They want to live like

00:11:01.200 --> 00:11:03.430
the fountain of youth; they're trying to

00:11:03.440 --> 00:11:05.670
become immortal.

00:11:05.680 --> 00:11:07.190
And that's what the Lord was showing me:

00:11:07.200 --> 00:11:08.870
they were trying to do it through

00:11:08.880 --> 00:11:11.430
AI technology. "How do we splice it? How

00:11:11.440 --> 00:11:12.870
do we inject this, like the fountain

00:11:12.870 --> 00:11:12.880
of—if

00:11:12.880 --> 00:11:14.710
we drink this, will it make us

00:11:14.720 --> 00:11:16.230
better? Will it make us stronger? Will

00:11:16.240 --> 00:11:18.790
it make us live

00:11:18.790 --> 00:11:18.800
longer?"And

00:11:18.800 --> 00:11:20.310
they were trying to do that through

00:11:20.320 --> 00:11:22.470
AI. The Lord told me, "Brandon,

00:11:22.480 --> 00:11:24.150
there's a time to sow and there's a time

00:11:24.160 --> 00:11:26.150
to reap. There's a time to live and

00:11:26.160 --> 00:11:28.310
there's a time to die. There's no man

00:11:28.320 --> 00:11:30.069
that's ever going to live forever on

00:11:30.079 --> 00:11:33.030
this earth right now."And as they try

00:11:33.040 --> 00:11:35.670
to create what they're doing,

00:11:35.680 --> 00:11:38.790
they're trying to bypass

00:11:38.790 --> 00:11:38.800
seedtime

00:11:38.800 --> 00:11:41.430
and harvest.

00:11:44.320 --> 00:11:47.350
I saw them taking

00:11:47.360 --> 00:11:50.310
genetics from a starfish and worms,

00:11:50.320 --> 00:11:53.829
trying to figure out how to splice that

00:11:53.839 --> 00:11:57.750
and make things that grow arms, grow back

00:11:57.760 --> 00:12:00.069
