00:12:04.480 --> 00:12:06.230
It was very weird stuff that I was

00:12:06.240 --> 00:12:07.990
seeing. And then I was seeing them

00:12:08.000 --> 00:12:11.030
trying to create a superfood that was

00:12:11.040 --> 00:12:14.150
