It looked like a little nut. It

00:12:26.870 --> 00:12:26.880
truly

00:12:26.880 --> 00:12:29.430
did—a genetically

00:12:29.430 --> 00:12:29.440
modified-looking

00:12:29.440 --> 00:12:32.550
nut

00:12:34.399 --> 00:12:36.710
they

00:12:36.720 --> 00:12:38.550
called a superfood, trying to

00:12:38.560 --> 00:12:41.030
keep you alive by eating this, but there

00:12:41.030 --> 00:12:41.040
was

00:12:41.040 --> 00:12:43.430
no nutritional value in it. It's

00:12:43.440 --> 00:12:45.590
man-made.

00:12:45.600 --> 00:12:47.509
Anything man-made is not going to be good

00:12:47.519 --> 00:12:50.069
for you. I mean, seriously, if it's not

00:12:50.079 --> 00:12:52.389
vegetables or

00:12:52.389 --> 00:12:52.399
whatever—this

00:12:52.399 --> 00:12:54.870
is like something that's in a

00:12:54.880 --> 00:12:57.030
lab. They were trying to create it and

00:12:57.040 --> 00:12:59.269
it was gross, but they were

00:12:59.279 --> 00:13:00.790
adding things to it and trying to do

00:13:00.800 --> 00:13:02.550
things to it. They do that already

