man's mind and what they're trying to

00:13:12.399 --> 00:13:14.310
do, it just kind of throws you.

00:13:14.320 --> 00:13:16.790
You go, "Wow, how much

00:13:16.800 --> 00:13:21.430
darker can people really

00:13:21.430 --> 00:13:21.440
get?"There's

00:13:21.440 --> 00:13:23.990
a level that you think you won't

00:13:24.000 --> 00:13:27.190
cross with people. Are you all

00:13:27.200 --> 00:13:29.670
really going to go there, trying to

00:13:29.680 --> 00:13:31.670
create things like that? Well,

00:13:31.680 --> 00:13:33.509
there's no moral balance.

00:13:33.519 --> 00:13:35.509
There's no moral compass.

00:13:35.519 --> 00:13:37.829
Everything goes. We have the

